this is the notes for regularExpressions

When we want more control over filtering our strings we need to use 
regular expressions 

lets say we want to get courses who's author starts with vance 
to do this 
we passs a object in the find method and the value author
instead of using a string we pass a regular expression (please look at the find method in code)

we add a i to make it case insensitive so we can type it however we want 
